'''奇博克女学生遭绑架事件'''发生在2014年4月14日到4月15日夜间，尼日利亚[[博尔诺州|博尔诺州]]{{le|奇博克|Chibok}}镇官立中学（{{lang|en|Goverment Secondary School}}）276名女学生被绑架<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/06/23/nigeria-says-21-girls-in-boko-haram-kidnapping-still-missing|title=Nigeria says 219 girls in Boko Haram kidnapping still missing|publisher=Fox News|date=2014-06-26|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120113418/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/06/23/nigeria-says-21-girls-in-boko-haram-kidnapping-still-missing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大本营设在尼日利亚东北部的极端主义恐怖组织[[博科圣地|博科圣地]]声称对绑架负责。接下来的几个月内，57名女生设法逃脱<ref name = BBC20160414/>，部分人曾在国际人权会议上親述自己的遭遇<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xat2T31waGM|title= "I escaped Boko Haram" – A Nigerian girl who was kidnapped with 270 others ("Bring Back Our Girls")|date= 2015-02-25|accessdate= 2016-08-15|archive-date= 2018-04-14|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180414161925/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xat2T31waGM|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

自那时起各种场合都表达了剩下219名女生能获释的愿望<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.worldwatchmonitor.org/2014/10/article_3431199.html/|title=Claim of truce raises hope that kidnapped Nigerian girls will be released|date=2014-10-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024152804/https://www.worldwatchmonitor.org/2014/10/article_3431199.html/|archivedate=2014-10-24|accessdate=2016-08-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/breaking-news-chibok-girls-not-yet-rescued/189752/ |title=Chibok Girls Not Yet Rescued |date=2014-09-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024155721/http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/breaking-news-chibok-girls-not-yet-rescued/189752/ |archivedate=2014-10-24 |accessdate=2016-08-15 }}</ref><ref name="ExchangeScrapped"/>。新闻媒体报道称博科圣地希望利用女生作为谈判棋子，交换该组织一些在押的指挥官<ref name = BBC20160414/><ref name="Lamb"/>。2016年5月，其中一名失踪的女生阿米娜·阿里（{{lang|en|Amina Ali}}）被发现。她声称剩下的女生还在绑架地点，但有6个人死亡。该周晚些时候，又有一名女生被寻获，但家长们表达了她的名字不在最初失踪者名单上的疑惑<ref name="BBC" />。

== 背景 ==
{{main|博科圣地}}
激进组织博科圣地反对尼日利亚“西化”，将其视为该国犯罪行为的祸根<ref name=Telegraph>{{cite news|title=Extremist attack in Nigeria kills 42 at boarding school|first=Damien|last=McElroy|date=2013-07-06|work=Daily Telegraph|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/nigeria/10163942/Extremist-attack-in-Nigeria-kills-42-at-boarding-school.html|accessdate=2013-10-03|archive-date=2013-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818043830/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/nigeria/10163942/Extremist-attack-in-Nigeria-kills-42-at-boarding-school.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而该组织制造的多起袭击事件造成成千上万的民众遇害，尼日利亚联邦政府于2013年5月曾宣布博尔诺州进入紧急状态，以打击该地的叛乱分子<ref name=AFP>{{cite news|title=Nigeria school attack claims 42 lives|agency=AFP|work=The Australian|date=2013-07-06|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/nigeria-school-attack-claims-42-lives/story-e6frg6so-1226675417375|accessdate=3 October 2013|archive-date=2013-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221060730/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/nigeria-school-attack-claims-42-lives/story-e6frg6so-1226675417375|dead-url=no}}</ref>。数百名叛乱分子被捕或被杀，餘下的叛亂分子逃向山区，并向平民發動襲撃<ref name=Newsday>{{cite news|last=Adamu|first=Adamu|last2=Faul|first2=Michelle|title=School attack kills 30 in northeast Nigeria|date=2013-06-06|agency=AP|work=Newsday|url=http://www.newsday.com/news/30-killed-in-school-attack-in-nigeria-1.5638194|accessdate=2013-10-03|archive-date=2013-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005082604/http://www.newsday.com/news/30-killed-in-school-attack-in-nigeria-1.5638194|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这场稳定国家的运动未有達成目標，另一方面，[[马里北部冲突|法国在马里的军事行动]]将博科圣地和[[基地组织|基地组织]]恐怖分子赶进尼日利亚<ref name=USAToday />。

自2010年以来，博科圣地有针对性在学校策划恐怖袭击，杀死数百名学生。该组织的发言人扬言，只要尼日利亚政府敢-{干}-涉伊斯兰教传统教育，突如而来的袭击就会持续下去，这使得10000名儿童因恐怖活动而无法入学<ref name=Telegraph/>。博科圣地还将无法接受教育的女孩绑架，强制她们当厨师或[[性奴|性奴]]<ref name=USAToday />。

博科圣地的袭击在2014年愈演愈烈。2月份，该组织在多伦巴嘎及伊格兹村砍杀100名信奉基督教村民<ref name=USAToday />。同月，尼日利亚东北部{{link-en|联邦政府学院袭击|Federal Government College attack}}导致59名学生遇害<ref name=theguardian-article>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram kills 59 children at Nigerian boarding school|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/feb/25/boko-haram-kills-children-boarding-school|accessdate=2014-03-06|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2014-02-25|archive-date=2014-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226141016/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/feb/25/boko-haram-kills-children-boarding-school|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本次绑架案系发生在造成至少88人死亡的[[2014年4月阿布加炸彈爆炸事件|阿布贾爆炸袭击]]的同一天<ref name=GuardApr23>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2014/apr/23/200-girls-missing-nigeria-care-sewol-tragedy|title=200 girls are missing in Nigeria – so why doesn't anybody care?|author=Anne Perkins|publisher=The Guardian|date=2014-04-23|accessdate=2014-04-23|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423200811/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2014/apr/23/200-girls-missing-nigeria-care-sewol-tragedy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2014年，该组织策划袭击造成近4000人死亡<ref name=USAToday />。[[伊斯兰马格里布基地组织|伊斯兰马格里布基地组织]]和[[基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支|基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支]]向博科圣地提供培训，帮助博科圣地加紧袭击步伐<ref name=sell/>。

== 绑架过程 ==
[[File:Chibok_kidnapping_destruction_VOA.jpg|thumbnail]]
2014年4月14日到4月15日晚，一队武装分子袭击了尼日利亚奇博克的官立女子中学（{{lang|en|Government Girls Secondary School}}）。他们假扮成警卫闯入学校<ref name=GuardApr19>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/apr/19/88-nigerian-schoolgirls-abducted-by-islamic-extremists-still-missing|title=88 Nigerian schoolgirls abducted by Islamic extremists still missing|agency=Associated Press|work=The Guardian|date=2014-04-19|accessdate=2014-04-23|archive-date=2014-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422181259/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/apr/19/88-nigerian-schoolgirls-abducted-by-islamic-extremists-still-missing|dead-url=no}}</ref>，让女孩们跟他们出去<ref name=TheTimes/>。大量学生被卡车载走，可能进入了博科圣地设要塞大本营的{{le|撒比萨森林|Sambisa Forest}}{{le|孔杜加|Konduga}}地区<ref name=GuardApr19/>。奇博克镇的房子也在事件中被烧毁<ref name=TheTimes>Maclean, Ruth (17 April 2014) [http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4066295.ece -{Nigerian schoolgirls still missing after military ‘fabricated’ rescue}-] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4066295.ece |date=20170203054740 }} The Times, (may need a subscription to view online), Retrieved 10 May 2014</ref>。袭击发生前四个星期，学校曾鉴于安全局势恶化关闭了学校，但多间学校的学生被召前来参加物理课的期末考试<ref name=GuardApr23/><ref>{{cite news|title=230 schoolgirls still missing after Boko Haram raid|url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/africa/2014/04/22/230-schoolgirls-still-missing-after-boko-haram-raid|accessdate=2014-04-27|newspaper=Times Live|date=2014-04-22|archive-date=2014-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427051731/http://www.timeslive.co.za/africa/2014/04/22/230-schoolgirls-still-missing-after-boko-haram-raid|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=VOA52/>。

来自多个村庄的530名学生报名参加了高中会考，但袭击发生时在场学生的人数还不明确<ref name=AA52/>。学生年龄在16岁到18岁左右，都是毕业生<ref name=BBC/>。最初的报道称有85名学生在袭击中被绑架。但到了4月19日到20日周末，军方发表声明表示129名被绑女生中，已有100多名获释。然而，声明于4月21日收回，家长表示有234名女生失踪<ref name=USAToday/> 。许多从两组绑匪手中逃脱<ref>{{cite news|title=Chibok abductions in Nigeria: 'More than 230 seized'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27101714|accessdate=2014-04-26|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-04-21|archive-date=2016-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531064708/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27101714|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方表示，大约276名孩子在袭击中被带走，截至5月2日，已有53人逃脱<ref name=AA52/>。另有报道称被绑女生共329名，有53名逃脱，276人仍然下落不明<ref>{{cite news|title=Nigerian school says 329 girl pupils missing|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4079819.ece|publisher=Times|date=2014-05-03|accessdate=2014-05-10|archive-date=2017-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208033452/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4079819.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=United States Sending Manned Flights Over Nigeria to Look for Girls|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/missing-nigeria-schoolgirls/united-states-sending-manned-flights-over-nigeria-look-girls-n103701|newspaper=ABC news|accessdate=2014-10-21|archive-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214062909/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/missing-nigeria-schoolgirls/united-states-sending-manned-flights-over-nigeria-look-girls-n103701|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[国际特赦组织|国际特赦组织]]表示尼日利亚军方曾接到提前四小时的绑架预警，但没有派出援兵保护学校<ref name=BBCMay9>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-27344863|title=Nigeria abductions: Warnings of school raid 'ignored'|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-05-09|accessdate=2014-05-09|archive-date=2014-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140509171820/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-27344863|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尼日利亚军方证实了这一说法，但他们表示军队需要防守的地方太多，无法调动增援<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/nigeria-hour-warning-school-raid-amnesty-international/story?id=23652165|publisher=ABC News|title=Nigeria Had 4-Hour Warning on School Raid, Amnesty International Says|author=Hamish MacDonald and Bola Omisore|date=2014-05-09|accessdate=2016-08-15|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815223714/http://abcnews.go.com/International/nigeria-hour-warning-school-raid-amnesty-international/story?id=23652165|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[伦敦大学国王学院|伦敦大学国王学院]]教授乔纳森·N·C·希尔（{{lang|en|Jonathan N.C. Hill}}）指出，博科圣地组织绑架这些女孩，是受了伊斯兰马格里布基地组织与日俱增的影响，并声称该组织的目标是利用女童和年轻妇女作为性对象，充当恐吓平民不反抗的手段。希尔表示袭击类似于阿尔及利亚上世纪90年代和21世纪初的绑架案<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hill|first1=Jonathan N.C.|title=Boko Haram, the Chibok Abductions and Nigeria’s Counterterrorism Strategy|journal=Combatting Terrorism Center at West Point|date=2014-07-30|url=https://www.ctc.usma.edu/posts/boko-haram-the-chibok-abductions-and-nigerias-counterterrorism-strategy|accessdate=2014-09-04|archive-date=2014-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904160609/https://www.ctc.usma.edu/posts/boko-haram-the-chibok-abductions-and-nigerias-counterterrorism-strategy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Marina Lazreg, "Consequences of Political Liberalisation and Sociocultural Mobilisation for Women in Algeria, Egypt and Jordan," in Anne-Marie Goetz, Governing Women: Women’s Political Effectiveness in Contexts of Democratisation and Governance Reform (New York: Routledge/UNRISD, 2009), p. 47.</ref>。

== 后续 ==

[[File:CEE-HOPE_NIGERIA_FOR_WIKI_LOVES_WOMEN"S_PROJECT_IN_NIGERIA_13.jpg|thumb]]
非穆斯林学生被迫皈依伊斯兰教<ref name=csmonitor1>{{cite news|author=Howard LaFranchi|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Foreign-Policy/2014/0505/What-role-for-US-in-efforts-to-rescue-Nigeria-s-kidnapped-girls-video|title=What role for US in efforts to rescue Nigeria's kidnapped girls?|publisher=CSMonitor|date=2014-05-05|accessdate=2014-05-09|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326073323/http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Foreign-Policy/2014/0505/What-role-for-US-in-efforts-to-rescue-Nigeria-s-kidnapped-girls-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每位女生以所谓的2000[[尼日利亚奈拉|奈拉]]（约合12.5[[美元|美元]]、7.5[[欧元|欧元]]）“[[聘礼|聘礼]]”被迫嫁给博科圣地分子<ref>{{cite news|url=http://therainbow.com.ng/boko-haram-kidnapped-the-230-school-girls-as-wives-for-its-insurgents/|title=Boko Haram kidnapped the 230 school girls as wives for its insurgents|work=The Rainbow|date=2014-04-29|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326073328/http://therainbow.com.ng/boko-haram-kidnapped-the-230-school-girls-as-wives-for-its-insurgents/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=TelegApr30>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/nigeria/10797454/Nigeria-kidnapped-schoolgirls-sold-as-wives-to-Islamist-fighters.html|title=Nigeria: kidnapped schoolgirls 'sold as wives to Islamist fighters'|first=Laura|last=Heaton|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2014-04-30|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-date=2014-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140501192253/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/nigeria/10797454/Nigeria-kidnapped-schoolgirls-sold-as-wives-to-Islamist-fighters.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。许多学生被带到邻国[[乍得|乍得]]和[[喀麦隆|喀麦隆]]，有学生与武装分子穿越边境的目击报告，住在撒比萨森林附近的村民也目击到学生<ref name=TelegApr30/><ref>{{cite news|first1=Turaki A|last1=Hassan|first2=Ibrahim Kabiru|last2=Sule|first3=Ronald|last3=Mutum|url=http://dailytrust.info/index.php/top-stories/22791-abducted-girls-moved-abroad|title=Abducted girls moved abroad|work=Daily Trust|date=2014-04-29|accessdate=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506232533/http://www.dailytrust.info/index.php/top-stories/22791-abducted-girls-moved-abroad|archive-date=2014-05-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。森林被认为是博科圣地的避难所<ref name=TelegApr30/>。当地居民在尼日利亚东北部联系人的帮助下，已追踪到学生的移动路径<ref name=TelegApr30/>。

2014年5月2日，警方表示他们还不清楚被绑学生的确切人数。鉴于学生记录在袭击中受损，他们要求家长提供文件，以制作官方统计数据<ref name=AA52>{{cite news|title=Nigerian Police Begin Documentation of Kidnapped Girls|work=Premium Times|publisher=All Africa|date=2014-05-02|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201405021865.html|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-date=2016-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102004903/http://allafrica.com/stories/201405021865.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月4日，尼日利亚总统[[古德勒克·乔纳森|古德勒克·乔纳森]]首次就绑架事件公开讲话，他表示政府正想尽一切办法寻找失踪的女生<ref name=BBC/>。同时，他指责父母不向警方提供关于他们失踪孩子的充分资料<ref name= sell/>。

5月5日，博科圣地领导人[[阿布巴卡尔·谢考|阿布巴卡尔·谢考]]在一段视频声称对发生的绑架事件负责。谢考表示：“真主给我指示要卖掉她们......我要执行祂的指令”<ref name =BBC>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-27283383|title=Boko Haram admits abducting Nigeria girls from Chibok|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-05-05|accessdate=2014-05-05|archive-date=2014-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505160625/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-27283383|dead-url=no}}</ref>，“{{le|伊斯兰教对奴隶的看法|Islamic views on slavery|我的宗教允许奴隶制}}”，“我要抓走人们，让她们当[[奴隶|奴隶]]<ref name=CNNEssenceTerror>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/05/06/world/africa/nigeria-boko-haram-analysis/|agency=[[CNN|CNN]]|title=Boko Haram: The essence of terror|last=Lister|first=Tim|date=2014-05-06|accessdate=2014-05-13|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403100921/https://www.cnn.com/2014/05/06/world/africa/nigeria-boko-haram-analysis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”他表示，女孩们不应该上学，应该嫁人，因为女孩到了九岁就适合结婚<ref name=BBC/><ref name=CNNEssenceTerror/>。之后，博科圣地再度从尼日利亚东北部绑架了8名年龄在12岁到15岁之间的女生<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-05-06/an-boko-haram-kidnap-more-girls-in-nigeria/5435050|title=Boko Haram kidnaps more girls in Nigeria|date=2014-05-06|publisher=ABC News|place=AU|accessdate=2014-05-10|archive-date=2014-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511102650/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2014-05-06/an-boko-haram-kidnap-more-girls-in-nigeria/5435050|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该数目后来增至11名<ref>[http://nypost.com/2014/05/11/boko-haram-kidnaps-more-children-kills-villagers-in-nigeria/ Boko Haram kidnaps more children, kills villagers in Nigeria.] {{Wayback|url=http://nypost.com/2014/05/11/boko-haram-kidnaps-more-children-kills-villagers-in-nigeria/ |date=20160625174647 }} Sabrina Ford, Laura Italiano and Post Wires; [[New_York_Post|New York Post]], 11 May 2014 1:35am.</ref>。奇博克是[[基督教|基督教]]徒占主导的村庄，谢考承认抓了许多不是穆斯林的女生：“女生们没有接受伊斯兰教，她们现在群聚在一起......我们会用[[穆罕默德|先知穆罕默德]]对待他所抓异教徒的办法对待她们<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/13/world/africa/boko-haram-video-kidnapped-nigerian-girls.html?hpw&rref=world&_r=0 New York Times: "Nigerian Girls Seen in Video From Militants" By ADAM NOSSITERMAY] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/13/world/africa/boko-haram-video-kidnapped-nigerian-girls.html?hpw&rref=world&_r=0 |date=20141023164956 }} 13 May 2014</ref><ref name=NYTKibaku>[http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/15/world/africa/tales-of-escapees-in-nigeria-add-to-worries-about-other-kidnapped-girls.html New York Times: "Tales of Escapees in Nigeria Add to Worries About Other Kidnapped Girls" by Adam Nossiter] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/15/world/africa/tales-of-escapees-in-nigeria-add-to-worries-about-other-kidnapped-girls.html |date=20160819021154 }} 15 May 2014 |''"Most of the Chibok residents are Christians of a small minority group who speak Kibaku, another of Nigeria's myriad languages."''</ref><ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/may/14/nigeria-launches-military-operation-to-find-kidnapped-girls The Guardian: "Military operation launched to locate kidnapped Nigerian girls" by David Smith] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/may/14/nigeria-launches-military-operation-to-find-kidnapped-girls |date=20160725170002 }} 14 May 2014 | ''"Although most of the abducted girls are Christian, all were wearing Muslim dress and two were singled out to say they had converted to Islam."''</ref><ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27389082 BBC: "Nigeria abduction video: Schoolgirls 'recognised'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27389082 |date=20160711071247 }} 13 May 2014 |''"The girls' families have said that most of those seized are Christians, although there are a number of Muslims among them."''</ref>。”当日，附近城镇{{le|刚波鲁|Gamboru|刚波鲁恩加拉}}在尼日利亚安全部队离开當地出发搜索被绑学生后，遭到{{le|2014年刚波鲁恩加拉袭击|2014 Gamboru Ngala attack|博科圣地武装分子袭击}}，至少300名居民遇害<ref name="hp">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/05/07/boko-haram-attack_n_5279662.html|title=Boko Haram Attack Kills Hundreds In Border Town|work=The Huffington Post]|accessdate=2014-05-07|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307025038/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/05/07/boko-haram-attack_n_5279662.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月9日，前博科圣地谈判代表{{le|谢胡·萨尼|Shehu Sani}}表示该组织希望用被绑女生交换他们在押的成员<ref>{{cite web|title=Boko Haram wants to swap 300 kidnapped girls for jailed members|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/05/boko-haram-wants-to-swap-300-kidnapped-girls-for-jailed-members/|work=IANS|publisher=news.biharprabha.com|accessdate=2014-05-10|archive-date=2014-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512011115/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/05/boko-haram-wants-to-swap-300-kidnapped-girls-for-jailed-members/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月11日，尼日利亚[[博尔诺州|博尔诺州]]州长{{le|卡西姆·谢蒂马|Kashim Shettima}}表示，他曾目击被绑女生没有穿越喀麦隆或乍得边境<ref name="kashim">{{cite web|title=Nigerian governor says he sighted 200 abducted girls|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/05/nigerian-governor-says-he-sighted-200-abducted-girls/|work=IANS|publisher=news.biharprabha.com|accessdate=2014-05-12|archive-date=2014-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512230111/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/05/nigerian-governor-says-he-sighted-200-abducted-girls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月12日，博科圣地发布视频要求换俘并展示130名被绑女生，她们均包裹着[[希贾布|希贾布]]和长长的[[罩袍|罩袍]]<ref>{{cite web|title=New Video by Boko Haram shows 130 Kidnapped Nigerian girls|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/05/new-video-by-boko-haram-shows-130-kidnapped-nigerian-girls/|work=IANS|publisher=news.biharprabha.com|accessdate=2014-05-12|archive-date=2014-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140513012506/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/05/new-video-by-boko-haram-shows-130-kidnapped-nigerian-girls/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2626019/We-know-Nigerian-governor-claims-intelligence-missing-schoolgirls-leader-Anglican-church-says-talks-need-start-Boko-Haram-back.html|work=Daily Mail|title=Paraded by a blood-crazed fanatic, the terrified schoolgirl captives: Boko Haram release chilling videos of missing Nigerian girls as they reveal they have all been forced to convert to Islam|author=Ted Thornhill|author2=Jack Doyle|author3=Jason Groves|author4=Andrew Malone|date=2014-05-12|accessdate=2016-08-16|archive-date=2016-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516180106/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2626019/We-know-Nigerian-governor-claims-intelligence-missing-schoolgirls-leader-Anglican-church-says-talks-need-start-Boko-Haram-back.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

晚些时候在5月24日，由于总统古德勒克·乔纳森与美国、以色列、法国和英国外长在巴黎协商，达成不应向恐怖分子妥协而作交易，需要動用武力的解决方案的共识，一场以记者做中间人的确保获释女生交换100名在尼日利亚多所监狱被關押的博科圣地成員的交易因此被取消<ref name="ExchangeScrapped">{{cite news|title=Nigerian government 'called off deal' to free kidnapped girls|url=http://www.nigeriasun.com/index.php/sid/222347979/scat/8db1f72cde37faf3/ht/Nigerian-government-called-off-deal-to-free-kidnapped-girls|accessdate=2014-05-27|work=Nigeria Sun|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528021909/http://www.nigeriasun.com/index.php/sid/222347979/scat/8db1f72cde37faf3/ht/Nigerian-government-called-off-deal-to-free-kidnapped-girls|archive-date=2014-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

5月26日，尼日利亚首席国防参谋长宣布军方已定位到被绑的女生，但因担心间接伤害而没执行军方营救行动<ref name="BBC 26 May 2014">{{cite news|title=Nigeria army 'knows where Boko Haram are holding girls'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27582873|accessdate=2014-05-27|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-05-26|archive-date=2014-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527023132/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-27582873|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月30日，据报道尼日利亚东北部巴勒（{{lang|en|Baale}}）地区的民兵发现两名被强奸的受绑女生“半死不活”地绑在树上<ref>[http://www.theparadigmng.com/?p=18056 #BringBackOurGirls: Two Chibok Girls Raped And Left To Die In Sambisa Forest By Boko Haram.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theparadigmng.com/?p=18056 |date=20150129154600 }} The Paradigm; 19 May 2014.</ref><ref name=Spegel>Grill, Bartholomaus and Selander, Toby (30 May 2014) [http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/boko-haram-continues-to-terrorize-northern-nigeria-a-972282.html The Devil in Nigeria: Boko Haram's Reign of Terror] {{Wayback|url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/boko-haram-continues-to-terrorize-northern-nigeria-a-972282.html |date=20160915081728 }} Der Spiegel English edition, Retrieved 1 June 2014</ref>。村民表示博科圣地刚留下两个女孩，还杀害焚烧另外四个不听话的女生。223人仍下落不明<ref name=Spegel/>。

英国尼日利亚{{le|英联邦高级专员|High Commissioner (Commonwealth)|高级专员}}{{le|安德鲁·波考克|Andrew Pocock}}爵士表示，事发数月后美国天眼技术曾发现一群多达80人的女生，但没有采取行动。女孩们、一处营地和地面运输车辆的证据在撒比萨森林当地地标“生命之树”附近被发现<ref name = "Lamb"/>。

6月24日，据报道博尔诺州其他地区的另外91名妇女儿童被绑架<ref name=other>{{cite news|title=Islamist fighters 'kidnap 90 women and children' from Nigeria villages|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/nigeria/10922087/Islamist-fighters-kidnap-90-women-and-children-from-Nigeria-villages.html|accessdate=2014-06-25|work=The Telegraph|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625083453/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/nigeria/10922087/Islamist-fighters-kidnap-90-women-and-children-from-Nigeria-villages.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有消息估计6月份博科圣地在尼日利亚境外的三个大本营至少有600名女生<ref>Haynes, Deborah (9 June 2014) "More than 600 girls kidnapped by Boko Haram militants", The Times, Africa, also available on the internet with a subscription at [http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4112853.ece] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4112853.ece |date=20160817015338 }}</ref>。

6月26日，华盛顿特区公关公司利维克（{{lang|en|Levick}}）收到尼日利亚政府“一份价值120多万美元的合同”，让他们围绕奇博克女生绑架事件做“国际和地方媒体的公关”<ref>{{cite web|last=Wilson|first=Megan R|title=Nigeria hires PR for Boko Haram fallout|work=TheHill|accessdate=2014-06-30|date=2014-06-26|url=http://thehill.com/business-a-lobbying/210635-nigeria-hires-pr-for-boko-haram-fallout|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114201018/http://thehill.com/business-a-lobbying/210635-nigeria-hires-pr-for-boko-haram-fallout|archive-date=2015-11-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

7月1日，一名涉嫌参与女学生绑架案和尼日利亚东北部一处繁忙市场爆炸案的商人被警方抓获。军方消息说，他还被控协助伊斯兰激进武装组织杀害传统领导人伊德里萨·提姆塔（{{lang|en|Idrissa Timta}}）<ref>{{cite news|last=Ola|first=Lanre|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/01/us-nigeria-violence-idUSKBN0F63LL20140701|title=Bomb kills 20 in Nigeria market, girls' abduction suspect held|agency=Reuters|date=2014-07-01|accessdate=2014-07-07|archive-date=2014-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706144508/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/01/us-nigeria-violence-idUSKBN0F63LL20140701|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

7月15日，博科圣地高级成员、绰号“屠夫”的扎卡里亚·穆罕默德从巴勒莫森林（{{lang|en|Balmo Forest}}）附近的叛乱现场逃跑时，在达拉佐-巴斯利卡路（{{lang|en|Darazo-Basrika Road}}）被捕<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelstv.com/2014/07/15/police-arrests-another-high-ranking-member-boko-haram/|title=Police Arrests Another High Ranking Member of Boko Haram|work=Channels Television|accessdate=2016-08-16|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503173944/http://www.channelstv.com/2014/07/15/police-arrests-another-high-ranking-member-boko-haram/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/15/world/africa/nigeria-boko-haram-arrest/|title=Nigerian police say they've arrested senior Boko Haram member - CNN.com|author=Michael Pearson|date=2014-07-15|agency=CNN|accessdate=2016-08-16|archive-date=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207031429/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/15/world/africa/nigeria-boko-haram-arrest|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月12日，据报道最初被绑架的四名女生已逃跑，为逃命在尼日利亚走了三个星期。据称她们被关在喀麦隆的一个营地里，每天都被强奸<ref>Bonnici, Tom (12 October 2014), "Kidnapped Boko Haram girls make long walk to freedom", The Times, Africa, can also be accessed on the Internet with a subscription at [http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4234199.ece] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/world/africa/article4234199.ece |date=20151008024619 }}</ref>。

===2015年===
前圣公会牧师斯蒂芬·戴维斯（{{lang|en|Stephen Davis}}）成功联络三位博科圣地指挥官，他們表示有其他同黨願意釋放手上的奇博克女学生。戴維斯於2015年4月來到尼日利亚，他收到了女孩被强奸的视频证据，证明她们活着。他被告知有18人身患重病，有些人患上[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]。戴维斯拿到了博科圣地将释放患病少女的初步协议。有三次差點達成交易，可是每當他們準備把女孩帶到釋放地點時，就被另一组人阻止，认为可以利用她们赚钱。戴维斯最後因健康原因离开尼日利亚。戴维斯批評西方國家沒有努力營救女孩，他說定位那五或六个博科圣地主要营地並不困難，他在[[Google_Earth|Google Earth]]上就能找到，衛星追蹤或無人飛機找不到它們是難以置信<ref name = "Lamb"/>。

2015年5月，据报道尼日利亚军方已经收復大部分博科圣地此前占领的地区<ref>{{cite web|last=Corones|first=Mike|date=2015-05-05|url=http://blogs.reuters.com/data-dive/2015/05/05/mapping-boko-harams-decline-in-nigeria/|title=Mapping Boko Haram’s decline in Nigeria|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2015-05-06|archive-date=2015-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508011523/http://blogs.reuters.com/data-dive/2015/05/05/mapping-boko-harams-decline-in-nigeria/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，包括怀疑藏有奇博克女生的撒比萨森林的许多营地。尽管有许多妇女获释<ref>{{cite news|last1=Leithead|first1=Alastair|title=Boko Haram abductions: Freed 'bride' tells of stigma ordeal|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36041860|accessdate=2016-04-14|publisher=BBC News|date=2016-04-14|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415131032/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36041860|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但奇博克女生的踪迹还是没找到<ref>{{cite news|date=2015-05-04|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32574777|title=Boko Haram freed Nigerian women tell of captivity horror|work=BBC News, Africa|accessdate=2015-05-07|archive-date=2015-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507025337/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32574777|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据称部分女生被人用每位2000奈拉的价格卖为奴隶，其他人则被强迫嫁给博科圣地战士<ref>{{cite news |last=Omenaz |first=Ejikeme |date=2015-05-06 |url=http://dailyindependentnig.com/2015/05/boko-haram-chibok-girls-may-sold-slavery/ |title=Boko Haram: Chibok Girls May Have Been Sold Into Slavery |work=Daily Independent |accessdate=2015-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518065940/http://dailyindependentnig.com/2015/05/boko-haram-chibok-girls-may-sold-slavery/ |archivedate=2015-05-18 }}</ref>，她们或许已遇害<ref>{{cite news|last=Winsor|first=Morgan|date=2015-04-06|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/nigeria-chibok-kidnapping-boko-haram-likely-killed-schoolgirls-last-month-report-says-1870710|title=Nigeria Chibok Kidnapping: Boko Haram Likely Killed Schoolgirls Last Month, Report Says|work=International Business Times|accessdate=2015-05-07|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518121134/http://www.ibtimes.com/nigeria-chibok-kidnapping-boko-haram-likely-killed-schoolgirls-last-month-report-says-1870710|dead-url=no}}</ref>。博尔诺州州长卡西姆·谢蒂马怀疑女生被关在地下掩体里<ref>(20 Masy 2015) [http://www.nigerianwatch.com/news/7000-borno-state-governor-says-he-believes-chibok-girls-are-being-held-in-boko-haram-bunkers Borno State governor says he believes Chibok girls are being held in Boko Haram bunkers] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nigerianwatch.com/news/7000-borno-state-governor-says-he-believes-chibok-girls-are-being-held-in-boko-haram-bunkers |date=20160305121833 }} Nigeria Watch, Retrieved 23 May 2015</ref>。

===2016年===
2016年1月，尼日利亚军方据报已救出1000名被博科圣地关押的妇女<ref name="Suicide">{{cite news|last1=Searcey|first1=Dionne|title=Nigeria Vexed by Boko Haram’s Use of Women as Suicide Bombers|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/12/world/africa/nigeria-vexed-by-boko-harams-use-of-women-as-suicide-bombers.html?_r=0|accessdate=2016-03-23|publisher=New York Times|date=2016-02-11|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216074647/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/12/world/africa/nigeria-vexed-by-boko-harams-use-of-women-as-suicide-bombers.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但没有奇博克女生<ref name = "Lamb"/>。

2016年4月，博科圣地发布视频，展示15名疑似被绑的奇博克女生。视频显然是在2015年12月拍摄的，女生们似乎吃得饱，毫无压力<ref name="BBC20160414">{{cite news|title=Nigeria Chibok girls 'shown alive' in Boko Haram video|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36041635|accessdate=2016-04-14|publisher=BBC News Africa|date=2016-04-14|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414100053/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36041635|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月17日，其中一名女生阿米娜·阿里·尼克奇（{{lang|en|Amina Ali Nkeki}}）连同她的婴儿，以及自称是他丈夫的疑似博科圣地武装分子穆罕默德·海雅图（{{lang|en|Mohammad Hayyatu}}）被撒比萨森林的民間自衛隊“平民联合特遣部队”发现。三人均营养不良<ref name=bbc36321249/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/parents-raise-hopes-as-chibok-escapee-says-other-girls-alive-cpw7rpv3m|title=Parents raise hopes as Chibok escapee says other girls alive|last=Lamb|first=Christina|date=2016-05-22|website=The Times|location=U.K.|access-date=2016-05-23|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602205810/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/parents-raise-hopes-as-chibok-escapee-says-other-girls-alive-cpw7rpv3m|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她随后被带到辨认出她的部队领导者阿伯库·古奇（{{lang|en|Aboku Gaji}}）的家中<ref name=bbc36321249>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36321249|title=Chibok girls: 'First kidnapped girl found' in Nigeria|website=BBC News|access-date=2016-05-18|archive-date=2016-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518142316/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36321249|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她于5月19日会见了尼日利亚总统[[穆罕默杜·布哈里|穆罕默杜·布哈里]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36328583|title=Chibok girls: Amina Ali Nkeki meets President Buhari|website=BBC News|access-date=2016-05-19|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519165224/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-36328583|dead-url=no}}</ref>。政府官员当日宣布军方和民兵组织在5月19日的一次行動中击毙35名博科圣地武装分子，解救97名妇女和儿童，并声称其中一名妇女是奇博克女学生<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/20/world/africa/boko-haram-abducted-nigeria-schoolgirls-found-rescue-chibok.html |title=Another Chibok Schoolgirl Kidnapped by Boko Haram Is Found, Nigeria Says |accessdate=2016-08-16 |archive-date=2016-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725215220/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/20/world/africa/boko-haram-abducted-nigeria-schoolgirls-found-rescue-chibok.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，關注奇博克被擄女生下落的團體表示雖然这位名叫西拉·卢卡（{{lang|en|Serah Luka}}）的女孩是奇博克學校的學生，不過她是在其它地方被擄走而不是2014年4月14日被擄的219名女生之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Rescue groups say second Chibok kidnap victim found by Nigerian army was taken by Boko Haram after doubts were raised|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3599879/Second-Chibok-schoolgirl-abducted-Boko-Haram-two-years-ago-found.html|website=Daily Mail|accessdate=2016-08-21|date=2016-05-19|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806185742/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3599879/Second-Chibok-schoolgirl-abducted-Boko-Haram-two-years-ago-found.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36338989|title=Boko Haram abductees freed in Nigeria|date=2016-05-20|website=BBC News|access-date=2016-05-23|archive-date=2016-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522184334/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-36338989|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月21日，声称是博科圣地第二指挥官的埃米尔·穆罕默德·阿卜杜拉（{{lang|en|Amir Muhammad Abdullahi}}）声称只要他们不受伤害便投降，作为交换，他们会释放包括奇博克女学生在内的人质。不过他这样说奇博克女生：“......坦率地说，她们只有三分之一活了下来，剩下的都牺牲了<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/boko-haram-willing-to-release-more-chibok-girls-wzmq6js3h|title=Boko Haram willing to release more Chibok girls|last=Kelly|first=Jeremy|date=2016-05-21|website=The Times|publication-place=U.K.|access-date=2016-05-23|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602135920/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/boko-haram-willing-to-release-more-chibok-girls-wzmq6js3h|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

8月，博科圣地发布似乎关于约50名奇博克女生的视频，其中有些怀抱婴儿<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-37076644|title=Nigeria Chibok girls: Boko Haram video shows captives|last=|first=|date=2016-08-14|website=BBC News|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815001908/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-37076644|dead-url=no}}</ref>。持枪的蒙面发言人要求释放在押战士，以交换女孩。蒙面枪手表示一些女生已被尼日利亚的空袭杀害，有40人已成婚。影片显然是在博科圣地派系领导人之一阿布巴卡尔·谢考的指示下发布的<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/world/kidnapped-nigerian-girls-in-video-plea-for-freedom-bqcjns87c|title=Kidnapped Nigerian girls in video plea for freedom|last=Kelly|first=Jeremy|date=2016-08-15|website=|publisher=The Times|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815001404/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/world/kidnapped-nigerian-girls-in-video-plea-for-freedom-bqcjns87c|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月13日，尼日利亞政府宣佈，經過由[[國際紅十字會|國際紅十字會]]和[[瑞士|瑞士]]政府充當中間人的談判後，博科聖地釋放21名被綁架的奇博克女生<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-nigeria-security-girls-idUSKCN12D102 |title=Nigeria confirms release of 21 girls kidnapped in Chibok by Boko Haram |publisher=Reuters |date=2016-10-13 |accessdate=2016-10-13 |archive-date=2016-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013120141/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-nigeria-security-girls-idUSKCN12D102 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

11月5日，尼日利亞軍隊在博爾諾州發現另一名奇博克女生，她當時身邊有一名嬰兒。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://dailypost.ng/2016/11/05/breaking-another-chibok-girl-rescued-baby|title=Another Chibok girl rescued with baby|date=2016-11-05|newspaper=Daily Post|accessdate=2016-11-05|archive-date=2016-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106063205/http://dailypost.ng/2016/11/05/breaking-another-chibok-girl-rescued-baby|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/11/kidnapped-chibok-schoolgirl-nigerian-army-161105141146523.html|title=Kidnapped Chibok schoolgirl found by Nigerian army|date=2016-11-05|newspaper=Al Jazeera|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106055008/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/11/kidnapped-chibok-schoolgirl-nigerian-army-161105141146523.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBOGconfirm">{{cite news|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201611050291.html|title=Nigeria: #BringBackOurGirls Lauds Buhari, Army for Rescue of Another Chibok Girl|author=Opeyemi Kehinde|date=2016-11-05|newspaper=allAfrica|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106184625/http://allafrica.com/stories/201611050291.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="N24NGBBOGconfirm">{{cite news|url=http://www.news24.com.ng/National/News/bringbackourgirls-group-confirms-rescue-of-chibok-girl-maryam-ali-20161105|title=#BringBackOurGirls group confirms rescue of Chibok girl, Maryam Ali|date=2016-11-05|newspaper=News24 Nigeria|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106185254/http://www.news24.com.ng/National/News/bringbackourgirls-group-confirms-rescue-of-chibok-girl-maryam-ali-20161105|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2017年及以后 ===
2017年1月，尼日利亞軍隊找到另一名女生，她當時身邊有一名6個月大嬰兒。<ref name=CBS>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/nigerian-chibok-girl-kidnapped-by-boko-haram-found-baby-nearly-200-still-missing/|title=Nigerian girl kidnapped by Boko Haram, now a mother, found with baby|date=2017-01-05|work=Associated Press|publisher=CBS Newst|accessdate=2017-04-06|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407055225/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/nigerian-chibok-girl-kidnapped-by-boko-haram-found-baby-nearly-200-still-missing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/top-news/219713-bring-back-girls-group-confirms-identity-rescued-chibok-girl.html|title=Bring Back Our Girls group confirms identity of rescued Chibok girl|date=2017-01-05|first=Evelyn|last=Okakwu|newspaper=Premium Times|accessdate=2017-04-06|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407053859/http://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/top-news/219713-bring-back-girls-group-confirms-identity-rescued-chibok-girl.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>直至此時尚有195名奇博克女生下落不明。

2017年5月6日，博科聖地釋放82名奇博克女生，以換取政府釋放一些被捕的該組織成員。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-39833309 |title=Nigeria Chibok girls: Eighty-two freed by Boko Haram |work=BBC News |date=2017-05-07 |accessdate=2017-05-07 |archive-date=2017-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507043947/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-39833309 |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外綁架者在2016年10月和本次釋放中，共收到300萬歐元贖金。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/first-look-how-nigerias-kidnapped-schoolgirls-are-rebuilding-their-lives-1517584918|title=Nigeria Brought Back Its Girls—Now Comes the Hard Part|last=Parkinson|first=Joe|date=2018-02-02|work=Wall Street Journal|access-date=2018-02-03|last2=Hinshaw|first2=Drew|language=en|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2018-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202173223/https://www.wsj.com/articles/first-look-how-nigerias-kidnapped-schoolgirls-are-rebuilding-their-lives-1517584918|dead-url=no}}</ref>一名官員表示2017年5月原定有83名女生獲釋，但其中一人選擇留在其丈夫身邊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-39857474|title=Nigeria Chibok girls: 'One refused to be released'|date=9 May 2017|publisher=BBC|accessdate=10 May 2017|archive-date=2018-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104204943/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-39857474|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年1月4日，尼日利亞軍方宣佈在博爾諾州成功救出另一名女生。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigeria-confirms-chibok-girl-found-after-almost-four-years/articleshow/62370856.cms |title=Nigeria confirms Chibok girl found after almost four years |website=indiatimes.com |date=2018-01-04 |access-date=2018-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180222192229/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigeria-confirms-chibok-girl-found-after-almost-four-years/articleshow/62370856.cms |archive-date=2018-02-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2018年2月，尼日利亞的法院判處Haruna Yahaya入獄15年，是首次有博科聖地成員因為參與奇博克事件而被法院判刑。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-43045103 |title=Chibok girls kidnapper Haruna Yahaya jailed in Nigeria |work=BBC News |date=2018-02-13 |accessdate=2018-02-22 |archive-date=2018-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216183653/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-43045103 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年7月，另一名涉案者Banzana Yusuf被判入獄20年。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2018/07/13/africa/chibok-girls-kidnapper-jailed/index.html |title=Nigeria court jails second man involved in Chibok girls kidnapping |publisher=CNN |date=2018-07-13 |accessdate=2020-08-27 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915154424/https://edition.cnn.com/2018/07/13/africa/chibok-girls-kidnapper-jailed/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年1月，數名女生成功逃脫。<ref name="cnn20210129">{{Cite news|last=Busari|first=Stephanie|date=2021-01-29|title=Several remaining missing Chibok schoolgirls escape from Boko Haram|work=CNN|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/01/29/africa/nigeria-chibok-girls-escape-intl/index.html|accessdate=2021-08-02|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706033526/https://edition.cnn.com/2021/01/29/africa/nigeria-chibok-girls-escape-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年7月底，1名女生連同其丈夫向軍方自首。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/chibok-schoolgirl-freed-nigeria-seven-years-after-abduction-governor-says |title=Chibok Schoolgirl Freed in Nigeria Seven Years After Abduction, Governor Says |website=VOA |date=2021-08-07 |accessdate=2021-08-08 |archive-date=2021-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210808040129/https://www.voanews.com/africa/chibok-schoolgirl-freed-nigeria-seven-years-after-abduction-governor-says |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月14日，博爾諾州州長表示另一名女孩已重獲自由，州長辦公室表示她是向軍方自首。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/second-nigerian-chibok-girl-freed-week-seven-years-after-abduction |title=Second Nigerian ‘Chibok Girl’ Freed in a Week, Seven Years After Abduction |website=VOA |date=2021-08-14 |accessdate=2021-08-15 |archive-date=2021-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816001200/https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/second-nigerian-chibok-girl-freed-week-seven-years-after-abduction |dead-url=no }}</ref>

